= C4C rent a yacht to promote software patents =

----

''The day before the vote on the software patents directive, Simon Gentry from Campaign for Creativity has rent a boat with a banner asking to vote for the software patents directive. At the same time, people who were demonstrating in their trademark yellow "Power to the Parliament" t-shirts in front of the European Parliament hired some kayaks to counter the pro-software patents propaganda.''

